          "course_tag_name": "B.Des"
        },
        {
          "text": "Regular industry visit/field visit for better exposure and experience gain.",
          "name": "Sakshi Shankar",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Des"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college especially the kannur campus organises various activities every week to keep the fun going on.",
